1
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:10,300
=Dungeon Archive=

2
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:12,000
The killer is...

3
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,360
An Ke.

4
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:16,900
(Killer Confirmed: An Ke)

5
00:00:17,260 --> 00:00:20,100
(The Killer)

6
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:22,100
(Case reconstruction)

7
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:23,480
I'm the killer,

8
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:26,160
An Ke, from 2030.

9
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,240
A time traveler.

10
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:29,160
I was the glass factory heir.

11
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:31,160
But the An Residence was no mansion.

12
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,640
It was a furnace.

13
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,200
My dad, An Songqiu,

14
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,840
(No margin for error at the top)
believed fear was discipline.

15
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:38,040
I survived by obeying.

16
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:39,400
But I lived in terror.

17
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:41,320
Shaped by his abuse,

18
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,360
(Cry again, and I'll throw you out)
I raised my son, An Xiaoke,

19
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:45,320
(Talk back, and I'll beat you to death)
the same way.

20
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,600
In 2026,

21
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,000
Xiaoke vanished.

22
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,160
Only in 2030

23
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,840
did I find his body

24
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,680
(Dad, I won't go back anymore. By An Xiaoke)
and his hopeless final words.

25
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:54,840
Back home, I found

26
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:57,560
my dad's footage and sketches.

27
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,760
(Curse Victims: An San, An Si)
that was when I learned San and Si

28
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,160
weren't killed by any puppet curse.

29
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:03,720
They died from our dad's abuse.

30
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:06,360
(This is generational trauma)
I asked a parenting expert online.

31
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:09,720
They called it generational trauma.

32
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:11,560
What my parents left in me

33
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,960
would pass to my child.

34
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:16,080
On 24 March 2030,

35
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:17,720
in the family archive,

36
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:20,560
I stumbled upon a way
to travel through time.

37
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,760
All it took was paper.

38
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,600
Paper from any year

39
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,960
could take you there.

40
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,080
Use papers from different years,

41
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:30,840
mark each one with an X over an O,

42
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,320
then place them in the slot.

43
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,480
The matching timeline will open.

44
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,560
If I changed history before Xiaoke was born,

45
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,480
he might never exist.

46
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,720
So I could only go back to 2016,

47
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,640
(2016)
after his birth.

48
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,080
In 2016, I saw my younger self

49
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,360
hurting baby An Xiaoke

50
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,680
the same way.

51
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,680
That was when I decided

52
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,240
(I won't let this cycle continue)
to kill my past self.

53
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,080
(An Ke, 58)
My original timeline

54
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,240
could no longer be changed.

55
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,480
But in this timeline,

56
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,960
I could still raise An Xiaoke again.

57
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,680
(An Ke, 58. An Ke, 44)
As long as this version of me lived,

58
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:03,520
the 2030 tragedy would happen again.

59
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,560
Killing him and taking his place

60
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,640
was Xiaoke's only way out.

61
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,910
To protect my son
and expose the fake curse,

62
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:12,320
I used what I knew from 2030.

63
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,560
The secret room in the wine cellar,

64
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:16,360
the glass box matching the yard mirror

65
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,880
and the infrared detector that refreshed

66
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,720
(The infrared detector resets at 12AM)
at 12AM.

67
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,440
With them, I built a full setup

68
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:23,080
to clear myself.

69
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,920
The plan used the detector,

70
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,960
the drone, the yard mirror,

71
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,840
and the matching glass box

72
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,600
