77
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:45,840
That way,

78
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,120
everyone would assume

79
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,920
(Before 12AM)
the killer struck before 12AM.

80
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,240
(Tap to View History)
The logic was simple.

81
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,800
(25 Mar, 12AM–3PM: No life signs)
The infrared detector

82
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,600
