88
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,640
I was with them.

89
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,200
As long as I set it up early

90
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,280
(Only you, Mr. Wu, Mr. Jin, Mr. He,)
and had witnesses prove

91
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,800
(Ms. Wen, Mr. Ning, Mr. Ding, and Mr. Ke stayed)
