94
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,840
In that timeline,

95
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,680
I couldn't be the killer.

96
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,760
Once the plan was set,

97
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,960
I went to the 2030 study

98
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,360
