100
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,080
(24 Mar 2016, 9:50PM)
Then I traveled back again

101
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,560
to 24 March 2016,

102
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,880
