103
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,160
I went to the archive room.

104
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,360
(24 Mar 2016, 9:51PM)
At 9:51PM,

105
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,920
I walked out

106
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,720
