113
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:49,440
Once the lights went out,

114
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,360
I ran back and hid in my room.

115
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,640
(24 Mar 2016, 10PM)
At exactly 10PM,

116
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:55,120
