120
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,480
Because I knew

121
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,320
(The infrared detector resets at 12AM.)
the house's infrared detector

122
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,540
(25 Mar, 12AM–3PM: No life signs)
