123
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:07,880
So if I was seen before 12AM,

124
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:10,800
(Before 12AM)
it would be the perfect alibi.

125
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,200
(24 Mar 2016)
At 10:02PM,

126
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,080
I picked up the 2016 phone

127
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,160
