130
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,600
Then An Xiaowen came too.

131
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:23,520
Perfect. Another alibi witness.

132
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,000
(25 Mar 2016)
At 12AM on 25 March,

133
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,240
I ended the talk with Jin Xiangyu,

134
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,600
He Jiahuan, and An Xiaowen.

135
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,480
(25 Mar 2016)
At 12:10AM,

136
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:32,200
