142
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:45,520
I broke off two glass shards.

143
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Then used them to cut up his face.

144
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:51,480
I pushed the shards into his wounds.

145
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,400
To fake the first crime scene,

146
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,200
I flew the drone at 1AM

147
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,480
It carried the blood-filled box.

148
00:04:57,480 --> 00:05:00,960
I swung it into the big mirror
