all over the broken mirror.

151
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:07,640
It looked like the victim had hit it.

152
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,920
(25 Mar 2016)
At 1:05AM,

153
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,600
