154
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,000
But it was already past 12AM.

155
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:16,000
I couldn't go out to get it.

156
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,640
Luckily, the trees
were too tall to notice.

157
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,680
(25 Mar 2016)
At 1:06AM,

158
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:22,240
I saw An Yi coming downstairs.

159
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,920
Did he hear the drone?

160
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,720
I couldn't let him ruin this.

161
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,800
I hid and waited for him.

162
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,960
Then knocked him out.

163
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,560
I dragged him into the wine cellar too.

164
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,000
Then drugged him with Knockout drops.

165
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,600
Before he woke up,

166
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,000
