167
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,240
He never saw my face anyway.

168
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,760
He had no idea what happened.

169
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,880
(25 Mar 2016)
At 1:10AM,

170
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:43,560
