175
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,840
I grabbed a leaf from a nearby plant,

176
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,520
the same kind as the ones in the woods,

177
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,520
and tossed it into the fire.

178
00:05:57,520 --> 00:06:00,320
Then I rushed away.

179
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,480
When they found the burned body,

180
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:05,560
(Curse Victims: An San, An Si)
they'd think of San and Si.

181
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:08,440
They'd think the curse had returned.

182
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,160
(25 Mar 2016)
At 2AM,

183
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:12,760
I wore the puppet head
down to the fireplace.

184
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,880
By then, the body's face was burned.

185
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:17,440
I took it off and put it on him.

186
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,920
Then I realized my phone was gone.

187
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,360
It probably fell in the wine cellar.

188
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,320
But it didn't matter.

189
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,400
No one then would find that wine cellar.

190
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:25,280
Once it was done,

191
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,680
I went back and finally breathed.

192
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,480
I had finally killed him.

193
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,480
I would replace him.

194
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:33,120
With eyes that had seen hell,

195
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,520
I would protect that baby.

196
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,600
I would tear open the puppet curse lie

197
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,440
