199
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:44,800
It was their so-called education.

200
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:47,860
(Zhou Keyu player log archive)

201
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:48,580
(Identity Update: An Ke)

202
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,380
