218
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,880
That explained the leaves.

219
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,840
I thought,

220
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,120
yes. Exactly.

221
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,320
But I never expected

222
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:20,720
