223
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,600
I acted shocked.

224
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:21,920
What?

225
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,640
I pretended I knew nothing.

226
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,880
Later, in the hall,

227
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,960
