268
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:40,620
An Yi hadn't crossed me.

269
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:42,140
(An Ke had no reason to kill An Yi)

270
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,080
So I argued that none of us

271
