595
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:17,180
(Housekeeper: Jin Xiangyu, Cleaning Supervisor:
An Xiaoning, Janitor: An Xiaowen)

596
00:18:17,180 --> 00:18:17,680
(Janitor: An Ke, Bodyguard: He Jiahuan,
Security Guard: An Xiaoding)

597
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:20,800
I used to be a rich young lady.

598
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,320
