He was alive.

602
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:31,000
And his bones
would not develop red marks.

603
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,840
Not develop red marks.

604
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:34,000
So that body

605
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,960
