606
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:38,080
But weren't we all alive?

607
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:40,640
So I made a bold guess.

608
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,720
I killed myself.

609
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:42,500
(Bold theory)

610
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:44,640
From the 2030 clues,

611
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,480
we learned

612
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:47,080
(An Xiaoding: Physical abuse)
