613
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:48,760
(An Ke: Emotional abuse)
Dad's shadow,

614
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:50,360
(An Xiaowen: Cold violence)
we became another him.

615
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:51,280
(An Xiaoning: Verbal abuse)
For him,

616
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:51,840
