My husband,

657
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:03,120
He Jiahuan, was still with me.

658
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,560
Because I wasn't the killer,

659
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:06,880
I explained I was wandering

660
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,120
