661
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:08,900
(Explaining motive, lowering suspicion)

662
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,400
So I couldn't go back.

663
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:12,480
Between Ning and Ke,

664
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:14,560
(An Xiaowen's Suspect List)
I leaned toward Ke.

665
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:16,040
He was the one who called people

666
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,440
