673
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:29,640
I'm player Jin Jing.

674
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,960
I play the An family's lady,

675
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:32,920
Jin Xiangyu.

676
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:34,480
After the last case,

677
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:36,600
