689
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:56,040
Sounds scary.

690
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,160
A family curse?

691
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:59,520
I didn't buy it. Nonsense.

692
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:00,640
