Before dying, she made an X.

702
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:20,640
What did that mean?

703
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:22,320
(Curse Victims: An San, An Si)
Following the clues,

704
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,960
