708
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:32,440
(He accidentally killed An Si)
An Si was killed by accident.

709
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:35,880
(An Songqiu killed An Si by accident)
The puppet murder curse

710
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:38,800
