724
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,360
He was alive.

725
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,760
It had to be An Ke,

726
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,720
An Xiaoning,

727
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:07,840
An Xiaowen,

728
