765
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,320
For that reason,

766
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:22,560
I suspected An Ke more.

767
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,760
But later in the defense,

768
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:26,320
we used the timeline

769
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:29,240
