786
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,560
(Son of Jin Xiangyu and An Ke)

787
00:23:56,560 --> 00:23:57,420
(The loyal husband every girl wants)

788
00:23:57,800 --> 00:23:58,920
I'm He Jiahuan.

789
00:23:59,520 --> 00:24:01,080
After the first case,

790
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,280
