791
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:04,040
The child of Jin Xiangyu and An Ke.

792
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:06,640
I went from being their son-in-law
to being part of their bloodline.

793
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:09,280
Today, we met
at second floor as planned,

794
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:12,520
