795
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:13,760
But he never showed.

796
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:14,400
Smoke.

797
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:16,480
Instead, by the fireplace,

798
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:18,160
