799
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:21,520
There was an OX mark beside it.

800
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:24,320
The An family called it puppet murder.

801
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:25,520
But as a detective,

802
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:27,480
