803
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,360
I don't believe it.

804
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,240
I had to find the real killer.

805
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,520
But I never expected

806
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:33,240
